Class NodeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • sensor_network.NodeInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.ConnectionInfoI, fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.NodeInfoI, java.io.Serializable

    public class NodeInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.interfaces.NodeInfoI
    This class represents information about a sensor network node, including its range, ID, position, and endpoint descriptors. It implements the NodeInfoI interface.
